{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/react-and-rails-setup/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"julienneblogs"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bf264630-b954-5c96-b5c3-278d1f9a0f64","excerpt":"This is a guide for setting up a React frontend and Rails backend app. Set up React frontend Create React app In the terminal, go to your project directory Type…","html":"<p>This is a guide for setting up a React frontend and Rails backend app.</p>\n<h2>Set up React frontend</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create React app</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In the terminal, go to your project directory</li>\n<li>Type command - npx create-react-app client</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Set up proxy for local development</p>\n<ul>\n<li>After the React app is created, open package.json</li>\n<li>Add proxy property and give it the value of - <a href=\"http://localhost:8000\">http://localhost:8000</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 576px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/97849d01feeaffc2a6347dbdd785e80e/533c1/client-package-json.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.911392405063296%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"client package.json\"\n        title=\"client package.json\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/97849d01feeaffc2a6347dbdd785e80e/533c1/client-package-json.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/97849d01feeaffc2a6347dbdd785e80e/c26ae/client-package-json.png 158w,\n/blog/static/97849d01feeaffc2a6347dbdd785e80e/6bdcf/client-package-json.png 315w,\n/blog/static/97849d01feeaffc2a6347dbdd785e80e/533c1/client-package-json.png 576w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>That’s it for the frontend!</p>\n<h2>Set up Rails backend</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Set up REST API Rails backend</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In the terminal, go to your project directory</li>\n<li>Type command - rails new server —api -T</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Set up puma.rb</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open project in your code editor</li>\n<li>Open puma.rb\n<ul>\n<li>server > config > puma.rb</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Change the port that the server is listening to for requests from 3000 to 8000</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 512px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/578003280456e9e3883bef05c89f39db/01e7c/server-pumarb.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.36708860759494%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"server puma.rb\"\n        title=\"server puma.rb\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/578003280456e9e3883bef05c89f39db/01e7c/server-pumarb.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/578003280456e9e3883bef05c89f39db/c26ae/server-pumarb.png 158w,\n/blog/static/578003280456e9e3883bef05c89f39db/6bdcf/server-pumarb.png 315w,\n/blog/static/578003280456e9e3883bef05c89f39db/01e7c/server-pumarb.png 512w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p>Set up Gemfile</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open project in your code editor</li>\n<li>Open Gemfile\n<ul>\n<li>server > Gemfile</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Add gem ‘rack cors’</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 292px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/852ec4442256fa7e426974ca601ff865/2e9f9/server-gemfile.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.46835443037975%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"server gemfile\"\n        title=\"server gemfile\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/852ec4442256fa7e426974ca601ff865/2e9f9/server-gemfile.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/852ec4442256fa7e426974ca601ff865/c26ae/server-gemfile.png 158w,\n/blog/static/852ec4442256fa7e426974ca601ff865/2e9f9/server-gemfile.png 292w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 292px) 100vw, 292px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>In the terminal, go to project folder/server directory</li>\n<li>Type command - bundle install</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Set up cors.rb</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open project in your code editor</li>\n<li>Open cors.rb\n<ul>\n<li>server > config > initializers > cors.rb</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Add Rack::Cors code block</li>\n<li>Change origins to ‘localhost:3000’</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/8313892d64be54c29c2846d16121b824/218a4/server-corsrb.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.177215189873415%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"server cors.rb\"\n        title=\"server cors.rb\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/8313892d64be54c29c2846d16121b824/f058b/server-corsrb.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/8313892d64be54c29c2846d16121b824/c26ae/server-corsrb.png 158w,\n/blog/static/8313892d64be54c29c2846d16121b824/6bdcf/server-corsrb.png 315w,\n/blog/static/8313892d64be54c29c2846d16121b824/f058b/server-corsrb.png 630w,\n/blog/static/8313892d64be54c29c2846d16121b824/40601/server-corsrb.png 945w,\n/blog/static/8313892d64be54c29c2846d16121b824/218a4/server-corsrb.png 1052w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Notes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Starting React App</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In the terminal, go to your project/client directory</li>\n<li>Type command - npm start</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Starting Rails Server</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In the terminal, go to your project/server directory</li>\n<li>Type command - rails server s</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>React app will run on port 3000 and requests will be proxied to port 8000.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Rails server will run on port 8000 and accept requests coming from port 3000.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"React Frontend & Rails Backend Project Set Up","date":"July 05, 2021","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/crud-app/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CRUD App as Barebones App"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"bf264630-b954-5c96-b5c3-278d1f9a0f64","previousPostId":"ccb3dda1-3913-5e60-ac10-a77fc0338f38","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}